---
import data from "~/data/sites";
import { Icon } from "astro-icon/components";
---

<section class="relative grid grid-cols-1 text-center justify-items-center md:text-left md:grid-cols-[20rem_1fr] grid-rows-[14rem_1fr] md:grid-rows-none gap-8 md:gap-4 items-center justify-center text-slate-700 max-w-screen-lg mx-auto">
	<div class="header__left">
		<a href={data.github}>
			<img
				width="400"
				height="400"
				class="w-clamped h-clamped rounded-[10rem] border-2 border-rose-900 shadow-sharp"
				src="/kusamaxi_ascii.webp"
				alt="kusamaxi ascii logo"
				loading="eager"
			/>
		</a>
	</div>
	<div class="relative">
		<span class="text-base md:text-lg font-heading font-medium text-rose-700 uppercase tracking-wide">kusamaxi</span>
		<h1 class="relative block font-heading text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-zinc-900 leading-tight mb-3">
			So long suppression...
		</h1>
		<p class="text-base md:text-lg font-serif leading-relaxed text-slate-600 mb-4">
			Running validators outside corporate control. Building privacy tools that work. 
			Writing about plural AI, cryptography, and why centralization always fails.
		</p>
		<p class="text-sm md:text-base font-serif text-slate-700 mb-4">
			Every system tends toward control. We build the escape routesâ€”code that 
			can't be captured, networks that route around damage, ideas that refuse containment.
		</p>
		<!-- Add RSS link here -->
		<div class="mt-4">
			<a href="/rss.xml" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-rose-700 hover:text-rose-900 transition-colors">
				<Icon name="mdi:rss" class="w-5 h-5" />
				<span class="font-heading text-lg">RSS Feed</span>
			</a>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>
